{"tid":1356273,"cid":12,"subCid":0,"title":"剛剛將軍澳嘅小事一則","createTime":"2019-07-23T12:50:22.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-23T13:12:50.000Z","uid":82033,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"1f58ca52d91c15117705a821f2f3139ea9baf1a2","tid":1356273,"uid":82033,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T12:50:22.000Z","msg":"某間人氣連儂場餐廳<br />\n剛剛有個心口帶住巨玉嘅背心口臭肥大叔<br />\n瘋狂影相去一個有百幾人嘅簡體 Wechat group<br />\n<br />\n小弟溫馨提示佢：<br />\n「阿叔，你真係要小心啲，而家影呢啲相返大陸，有機會唔俾你過關，甚至乎扣留通後門都唔出奇...你都係小心啲好呀」<br />\n<br />\n點知佢雷霆大發，瘋狂大叫：<br />\n「我鍾意影咩相咪影咩相，犯咩法啊屌你老母。呢度香港黎架屌你老母，有種咪拉我囉，屌你老母」<br />\n「香港就係俾你呢啲垃圾癈青細路攪亂哂，屌你老母，信唔信我打柒你啊屌你老母」<br />\n<br />\n去到呢度...我大叫一句「阿叔上大陸叫雞小心啲啊」<br />\n<br />\n然後，我停咗幾秒，心諗...<br />\n點解我理解唔到佢啲logic嘅 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n影咩？咪下面呢啲：<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Ho84avg.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHo84avg.png&h=9e645ebd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n註：大約對白如上"},{"pid":"01d10849bb2a9dfa164046910b6595434c08993a","tid":1356273,"uid":212182,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T12:51:29.000Z","msg":"佢會有後果"},{"pid":"6b6c0f375b694c7b69b355b7c36b8698f91fd0bf","tid":1356273,"uid":82033,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T12:54:01.000Z","msg":"有冇在場巴打相認 <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b8293294c9431a5e923c7a6c9d33f21a25606546","tid":1356273,"uid":278712,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T12:59:55.000Z","msg":"支持樓主勇氣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a85a9ce0642ae9cce5c17032fa93d9d0bce2a187","tid":1356273,"uid":82033,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b8293294c9431a5e923c7a6c9d33f21a25606546","tid":1356273,"uid":278712,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T12:59:55.000Z","msg":"支持樓主勇氣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\"